{"tid":2164095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（美國對台售武）央視氣炸：一旦武統「首戰即終戰」","createTime":"2020-08-19T04:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T05:43:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"538e06ed752ce118118268cfa0f9e6a63b0219f7","tid":2164095,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T04:39:49.000Z","msg":"美國衛生部長阿札爾（Alex Azar）日前訪台，引發中國不滿。中國官媒《央視新聞》昨（18日）發表社論，指阿札爾訪台及美對台軍售使台海和平「亮紅燈」，宣稱「明天環島大演習甚至台灣上空演習也不是不可能」，還說「武統」一旦觸發，「首戰即終戰」。<br />\n<br />\n中國《央視新聞》昨晚發表題為「美台勾結挑釁必將遭到堅決打擊」的社論，指阿札爾訪台、美軍機穿台、美戰機貼近台灣偵查以及美國對台軍售等事件，使台海地區和平穩定亮起紅燈。中國解放軍近日台海軍演，是要對美國及台灣「秀肌肉」。<br />\n<br />\n《央視》社論進一步指稱，我國中科院在東部海域實彈射擊，是對台海局勢「火上澆油」，還嗆「台灣承受不起戰爭的後果」、「美國不是台獨的免死金牌」，並稱解放軍今天台海軍演，「明天環島大演習甚至台灣上空演習也不是不可能」，「武統」一旦觸發，「首戰即終戰」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3264796\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3264796&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInNnRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=eb11c2e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3264796&h=c0f756b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3264796</a>"},{"pid":"529203c63f907943e5ee746f121efeac9c73d49a","tid":2164095,"uid":314136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T04:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04fd09717bd8490eddcebf4327dd2bf7cca0d68","tid":2164095,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/0427be/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_190801/20190801_fc544267253aedece4b12NILH5RmuaVc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F0427be%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2F